headline: Value Meets Growth: 3 Artificial Intelligence (AI) Stocks Even Warren Buffett Might Respect
summary: This social media company could leverage its data horde to become an AI leader.  Investors often view value stocks and growth stocks as mutually exclusive.  This is likely because growth stocks often trade at premium valuations, and value stocks tend to attract conservative investors, or those focused on income more than growth.
